dynamics/discrete-time measurement models in MSOFE as opposed to the discrete-time dynamics equations employed in the AFIT software. The truth models and filter models used for MSOFE were identical except for the different tuning values that adjusted noise levels in the filter. The rFcader shi •Id review the next section for an understanding of the entire truth model and refer to Clhipter IV for the specific models used for MSOFE analyses.
